race.comment: CASPERNOVA (1) has been threatening all campaign and finds easier company with a handy 3kg claim. Rates strongly and gets his chance in this line-up. ONE BEAT NO BEAT (12) is also racing well enough and is back in grade. Has the blinkers on for the first time and may sit handier today. TORO STRIKE (11) just missed this track/trip last time and also has the blinkers applied for the first time. Third-up now and has been freshened. A live chance as well. SHOW ME MERCY (5) is hard to catch but good enough on his day. Maps well and has a 3kg claim and the blinkers go on again. Expect him to be around the mark.
